headline: Natural Gas Pipeline Capacity Ramping Up In Texas
summary: Texas is the center of US energy industry. Here we look at some pipeline projects in Texas under development, the themes driving investment, and companies that benefit from greater capacity.

headline: Navigator Gas: A Questionable $400 Million Decision (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Navigator Holdings has elected to construct four new ethylene capable medium gas carriers for $412 million. Find out why I have downgraded NVGS stock to a hold.
